Steps:
a. You start by creating a main div to hold the other div's (calculator).
b. You put input, add an id, and write 'readonly'. 
     <input id="display" readonly>
c. You create a div in calc (keys) and put button onclick.
    <button onclick="appenToDisplay('+')">+</button> (For all numbers and symbols)
    <button onclick="clearDisplay()">C</button> (To clear what is in the Display)
    <button onclick="calculate('=')">=</button> (To calculate)
Note: 1rem=16px
